text: Chistoperevoloka () is a rural locality (a village) in Levinskoye Rural Settlement, Bolshesosnovsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 14 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 10 km south- west from Levino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Bolshesosnovsky District
title: Chistoperevoloka
